title: Dishonored: Death of the Outsider [Update 1] (2017)
description:
Release date: September 15, 2017
Genre: Action, Shooter, Stealth, First-person, 3D
Developer: Arkane Studios
Publisher: Bethesda Softworks
Language: English

System requirements:
OS: Windows 7 and above (only 64 bits!)
Processor: Intel i5-2400 / AMD FX-8320 and better
Memory: 8 GB
Video: NVidia GTX 660 2 GB / AMD Radeon 7970 3 GB or better
DirectX: 11
Disk space: up to 24 GB (~ 27 GB for the time of repack installation)

Release info:
The repack is based on the ISO image DISHONORED.DEATH.OF.THE.OUTSIDER-STEAMPUNKS: stp-doto.iso
100% Lossless and MD5 Perfect: all files after installation are identical to the original release to within a bit (not counting remote locations)
Removed all the localizations, except Russian and English, NOTHING converted to anything.
After installation, the game takes up to 24 GB
After installation, the option to check the checksums of all files is available to make sure that the repack is installed correctly
The repack uses ZTool library from Razor12911

How to install:
Mount and install
Play
